flowchart TD
    A["💡 Spark: What if visuals beat words?"] --> B["🎯 Define the Thesis"]
    B --> C{"Choose the Medium"}
    C -->|"Text only"| D["❌ Ironic — proving visuals\nwith just words"]
    C -->|"Visual + Text"| E["✅ Practice what you preach"]
    E --> F["🔍 Pick a Diagramming Tool"]
    F --> G["Mermaid — text-based,\nLLM-friendly, free"]
    G --> H["🤖 Prompt an LLM"]
    H --> I["'Diagram the steps of\ncreating this very post'"]
    I --> J["📊 LLM Generates\nMermaid Code"]
    J --> K["🖼️ Render the Diagram"]
    K --> L["✍️ Write the Post\nAround the Diagram"]
    L --> M["📎 Attach Both:\nImage + Code"]
    M --> N["🚀 Publish on LinkedIn"]
    N -.->|"🔄 Reader recreates\nthis exact diagram"| H

    style A fill:#1a1a2e,color:#e0e0ff,stroke:#4a4a8a
    style E fill:#16213e,color:#e0ffe0,stroke:#4a8a4a
    style D fill:#2e1a1a,color:#ffe0e0,stroke:#8a4a4a
    style G fill:#1e3a2e,color:#e0ffe0,stroke:#4a8a6a
    style J fill:#1e2e3a,color:#e0f0ff,stroke:#4a6a8a
    style N fill:#1a2e1a,color:#e0ffe0,stroke:#4a8a4a
